name: Hacker Empress (cracker) empresshacker-concept-b
description:
Hacker Empress posted screenshots from the game Nioh 2, where she made herself in the character editor. I don’t know how true these screenshots are and whether there really is such a person, maybe it’s a group of hackers, but based on these screenshots and her description of herself, I created several models for Stable Diffusion.

I made about 70 images, trained one model for 50, and trained others for 20. One model is more stylized, the second is more photographic.

Use the images I provided for prompts examples.
